bilingual.source: Plus they can download movies and music at high speeds.
bilingual.target: 另外，他们可以高速下载电影和音乐。

bilingual.source: We can download software, documents, and images whenever we need them.
bilingual.target: 我们可以随时下载软件、文件和图片。

bilingual.source: If you are a sugar addict and aren't able to say no to chocolate or cola, you had better download it now!
bilingual.target: 如果你是糖瘾者，不能拒绝巧克力或可乐，你最好现在就下载它！

bilingual.source: Click the icon to start the download.
The new software is available for download.
I use bitcomet to download large files quickly.
bilingual.target: 我使用bitcomet（比特彗星，一款下载软件）快速下载大文件。

bilingual.source: If the download fails, you can retry it.
bilingual.target: 如果下载失败，你可以重试。

bilingual.source: You can download music from this website.
bilingual.target: 你可以从这个网站下载音乐。

list.abstract: download（英 [ˌdaʊnˈləʊd , ˈdaʊnləʊd]，美 [ˌdaʊnˈloʊd , ˈdaʊnloʊd]），英语单词，作动词为下载。作名词为下载；下载的文件。短语搭配有download progress（下载进度）。例句为“Children can download many games for free.（孩子们可以免费下载许多游戏。）” download相关反义词有upload。

yingyinNormal.en: And the only way to download the ledger is through the central computer terminal located there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下载这个账册的唯一方法就是通过那地方的中央计算机终端。

yingyinNormal.en: I know you started firing people before I could download all the files, but I'm staying here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道你们在我能下载所有文件之前就开始解雇人了，但我留在这儿。

yingyinNormal.en: They can upload and download data. Memories. At sites like the one you just destroyed. Yes!
yingyinNormal.zh: 上传和下载数据，这就是个记忆库，就和你刚才毁掉的那个一样，一点没错。

yingyinNormal.en: I want to apply this to the Ultron program, but Jarvis can't download a data schematic this dense.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想把这个用到奥创程序上，但是贾维斯下载不了密度这么大的数据原理图。

yingyinNormal.en: So theoretically, you could download your thoughts and memories into this computer and live forever as a machine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以理论上，你可以把思想记忆下载到这种电脑上，然后以机器的形态长生不死。

yingyinNormal.en: What, you stole our Bitcoin? Oh, calm down. All I did was sneak onto your computer and download your Bitcoin onto a flash drive. What?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你偷了我们的比特币吗？冷静。我只是偷偷登录了你的电脑把你们的比特币下载到U盘上了。什么？

yingyinNormal.en: It's an iCal download. She can put it right in her phone. And I thought we agreed that you'd have your conjugal visits in her apartment.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是个iCal[Apple电子日程表]下载啊，她可以直接下到手机里的。而且我想咱们说好了的，你们只在她那儿行房事。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

v. 使过载；使超载；使负担过重；使（电力系统）超负荷

word_family.mean: n. 重负；负载；负荷；压力；一大堆；大量；动力；活动部件阻力；最大装载量；桶

sense_info_list.en: copy or move programs or information into a computer's memory, especially from the internet or a larger computer

examination_example.sentence: For all the possibilities of our new culture machines, most people are still stuck in <highlight>download</highlight> mode.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于我们新文化机器的所有可能性，大多数人仍然停留在下载模式。

examination_example.sentence: All animals <highlight>download</highlight>, but only a few upload.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所有动物都下载，但只有一些上传。

sense_info_list.en: a file or set of files that has been downloaded; a computer program that has been or can be copied into a computer's memory
